text: The Bicske District () is a district in the north-eastern part of Fejér County, Hungary. Bicske is also the name of the district seat in the Bicske District. The Bicske District is located in Central Transdanubia. == Municipalities == The district has 2 towns, 1 large village and 12 villages.
